(428,	919,	'316.1	 Zaokrouhlování\n\n316.2	 Zaokrouhlete číslo <code><var>commafy( NUM )</var></code> na <var>TPLACE</var>.\n\n316.3	 Existují dva způsoby, jak příklad řešit.\n\n316.4	 První způsob: Podívejte se na <var>placesLeftOfDecimal[ -1 - PLACE ]</var> číslici <code><var>DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ]</var></code> a uvidíte, jestli zaokrouhlovat nahoru nebo dolů.\n\n316.5	 Protože je to <span data-if=\"DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ] > 5\">more than</span><span data-else>equal to</span> <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme nahoru, čímž získáme <code><var>ROUNDED</var></code>.\n\n316.6	 Protože je menší než <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme dolů, čímž získáme <code><var>commafy( ROUNDED )</var></code>.\n\n316.7	 Druhý způsob: Zamyslete se, který konec číselné řady je blíže k <var>NUM</var> - tento konec je označen modře.\n\n316.8	 Zaokrouhlete <code><var>commafy( NUM )</var></code> na <var>TPLACE</var>.\n\n316.9	 Existují dva způsoby, jak příklad řešit.\n\n316.10	 První způsob: Podívejte se na <var>placesRightOfDecimal[ 1 + PLACE ]</var> číslici <code><var>DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ]</var></code> a uvidíte, jestli zaokrouhlovat nahoru nebo dolů.\n\n316.11	 Protože je to <span data-if=\"DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ] > 5\">more than</span><span data-else>equal to</span> <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme nahoru, čímž dostaneme <code><var>ROUNDED</var></code>.\n\n316.12	 Protože je menší než <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme dolů, čímž dostaneme <code><var>commafy( ROUNDED )</var></code>.\n\n316.13	 Druhý způsob: Zamyslete se, který konec číselné řady je blíže k <var>NUM</var> - tento konec je označen modře.\n\n',	'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html data-require=\"math math-format graphie graphie-helpers\">\n<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <title>Zaokrouhlování</title>\n    <script src=\"../khan-exercise.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"exercise\">\n\n    <div class=\"problems\">\n        <div data-weight=\"2\">\n            <div class=\"vars\">\n                <var id=\"DIGITS\">shuffle( [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9], 5 )</var>\n                <var id=\"NUM\">+DIGITS.join( \"\" )</var>\n                <var id=\"PLACE\">randFromArray([ -2, -3 ])</var>\n                <var id=\"TPLACE\">placesLeftOfDecimal[ -PLACE ]</var>\n                <var id=\"ROUNDED\">roundTo( PLACE, NUM )</var>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"question\">\n                <p>Zaokrouhlete číslo <code><var>commafy( NUM )</var></code> na <var>TPLACE</var>.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"solution\" data-forms=\"integer, decimal\"><var>ROUNDED</var></div>\n\n            <div class=\"hints\">\n                <p>Existují dva způsoby, jak příklad řešit.</p>\n                <p>První způsob: Podívejte se na <var>placesLeftOfDecimal[ -1 - PLACE ]</var> číslici <code><var>DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ]</var></code> a uvidíte, jestli zaokrouhlovat nahoru nebo dolů.</p>\n                <p data-if=\"DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ] >= 5\">Protože je to <span data-if=\"DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ] > 5\">more than</span><span data-else>equal to</span> <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme nahoru, čímž získáme <code><var>ROUNDED</var></code>.</p>\n                <p data-else>Protože je menší než <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme dolů, čímž získáme <code><var>commafy( ROUNDED )</var></code>.</p>\n                <p>Druhý způsob: Zamyslete se, který konec číselné řady je blíže k <var>NUM</var> - tento konec je označen modře.</p>\n                <div class=\"graphie\">\n                    init({\n                        range: [ [ -0.06 * pow( 10, -PLACE ) , 1.3 * pow( 10, -PLACE ) ], [-1, 1] ],\n                        scale: [ 600 * pow( 10, PLACE ), 40 ]\n                    });\n                    numberLine( floorTo( PLACE , NUM   ), ceilTo( PLACE , NUM ) +  pow( 10, -( PLACE+2 ))  , round( pow( 10, -(PLACE + 1 ))) );\n                    style({ stroke: \"#FFA500\", fill: \"#FFA500\", strokeWidth: 3.5 });\n                    ellipse( [  10 * pow( 10, -( PLACE+1 )) * (NUM -  floorTo( PLACE , NUM   ))/pow( 10,- (PLACE) ), 0 ], [pow( 10, -PLACE ) / 100, 0.15]);\n                    label( [  10 * pow(10, -( PLACE+1 )) * ( NUM -  floorTo( PLACE , NUM ))/pow( 10,- (PLACE) )], NUM, \"below\");\n                    style({ stroke: \"#6495ED\", \"fill\": \"none\", strokeWidth: 3.5 });\n                    if( DIGITS[ 5 + PLACE ] >= 5 ) {\n                        ellipse( [ pow( 10, -PLACE ), -0.55 ], [pow( 10, - PLACE - 0.5 ) / 6.5, 0.35] );\n                    } else {\n                        ellipse( [ 0, -0.55 ], [pow( 10, - PLACE - 0.5 ) / 6.5, 0.35] );\n                    }\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div data-weight=\"3\">\n            <div class=\"vars\">\n                <var id=\"DIGITS\">shuffle( [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9], 6 )</var>\n                <var id=\"NUM\">+DIGITS.join( \"\" ) / 10000</var>\n                <var id=\"PLACE\">randFromArray([ 0, 1, 2 ])</var>\n                <var id=\"TPLACE\">placesRightOfDecimal[ PLACE ]</var>\n                <var id=\"ROUNDED\">roundTo( PLACE, NUM )</var>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"question\">\n                <p>Zaokrouhlete <code><var>commafy( NUM )</var></code> na <var>TPLACE</var>.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"solution\" data-forms=\"integer, decimal\"><var>ROUNDED</var></div>\n\n            <div class=\"hints\">\n                <p>Existují dva způsoby, jak příklad řešit.</p>\n                <p>První způsob: Podívejte se na <var>placesRightOfDecimal[ 1 + PLACE ]</var> číslici <code><var>DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ]</var></code> a uvidíte, jestli zaokrouhlovat nahoru nebo dolů.</p>\n                <p data-if=\"DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ] >= 5\">Protože je to <span data-if=\"DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ] > 5\">more than</span><span data-else>equal to</span> <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme nahoru, čímž dostaneme <code><var>ROUNDED</var></code>.</p>\n                <p data-else>Protože je menší než <code>5</code>, zaokrouhlujeme dolů, čímž dostaneme <code><var>commafy( ROUNDED )</var></code>.</p>\n                <p>Druhý způsob: Zamyslete se, který konec číselné řady je blíže k <var>NUM</var> - tento konec je označen modře.</p>\n                <div class=\"graphie\">\n                    init({\n                        range: [ [ -0.06 * pow( 10, -PLACE ) , 10.3 * pow( 10, -PLACE ) ], [-1, 1] ],\n                        scale: [ 600 * pow( 10, PLACE ), 40 ]\n                    });\n                    numberLine( floorTo( PLACE , NUM   ), ceilTo( PLACE , NUM ) +  pow( 10,- (PLACE+2 ))  , pow( 10,- (PLACE+1) ) );\n                    style({ stroke: \"#FFA500\", fill: \"#FFA500\", strokeWidth: 3.5 });\n                    ellipse( [  10 * pow(10,- (PLACE+1)) * (NUM -  floorTo( PLACE , NUM   ))/pow(10,- (PLACE) ), 0 ], [pow(10, -PLACE) / 100, 0.15]);\n                    label( [  10 * pow(10, -( PLACE+1 )) * ( NUM -  floorTo( PLACE , NUM ))/pow(10, -(PLACE) )], NUM, \"below\");\n                    style({ stroke: \"#6495ED\", \"fill\": \"none\", strokeWidth: 3.5 });\n                    if ( DIGITS[ 2 + PLACE ] >= 5 ) {\n                        ellipse( [ pow( 10, -PLACE ), -0.55 ], [pow( 10, - PLACE - 0.5 ) / 6.5, 0.35] );\n                    } else {\n                        ellipse( [ 0, -0.55 ], [pow( 10, - PLACE - 0.5 ) / 6.5, 0.35] );\n                    }\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n',	'rounding_numbers',	'2013-05-07 22:02:06'),
(276,	732,	'302.1	 Porozumění sloupcovým grafům 1\n\n302.2	 V Bradavicích jsou čtyři koleje: <var>toSentence( HOUSES )</var>. Sloupcový graf níže ukazuje, kolik bodů dnes získala každá z kolejí.\n\n302.3	 Kolik bodů získala kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> ?\n\n302.4	 Najděte sloupec pro kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> tak, že se podíváte na písmena uvedená pod každým sloupcem.\n\n302.5	 Porovnejte výšku sloupce s čísly nalevo.\n\n302.6	 Kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> obdržela <var>plural( VALUES[ INDEX ], \"house point\" )</var>.\n\n',	'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html data-require=\"math graphie graphie-helpers d3 word-problems\">\n<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <title>Porozumění sloupcovým grafům 1</title>\n    <script src=\"../khan-exercise.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"exercise\">\n    <div class=\"vars\">\n        <var id=\"HOUSES\"> [ \"Gryffindor\", \"Hufflepuff\", \"Ravenclaw\", \"Slytherin\" ]</var>\n        <var id=\"INDEX\">randRange( 0, HOUSES.length - 1 )</var>\n        <var id=\"VALUES\">shuffle( [ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5 ], 4 )</var>\n        <var id=\"DATA\">\n            (function() {\n                var ordinals = $.map( HOUSES, function( house, i ) {\n                    return house.charAt( 0 );\n                });\n\n                return { min: 0,\n                    max: 5,\n                    tickCount: 5,\n                    values: VALUES,\n                    ordinals: ordinals };\n            })()\n        </var>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"problems\">\n        <div>\n            <p>V Bradavicích jsou čtyři koleje: <var>toSentence( HOUSES )</var>. Sloupcový graf níže ukazuje, kolik bodů dnes získala každá z kolejí.</p>\n            <p class=\"question\">Kolik bodů získala kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> ?</p>\n            <div class=\"graphie\" id=\"barchart\">\n                var width = 5;\n                var height = 5;\n\n                init({\n                    range: [ [ -1, width + 1 ], [ -1, height + 0.5 ] ]\n                });\n\n                var pos = { lx: 0, ly: 0, width: width, height: height};\n                graph.barchart = new BarChart( DATA, pos );\n                graph.barchart.draw();\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"solution\" data-type=\"multiple\">\n                <span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\"><var>VALUES[ INDEX ]</var></span> house points\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"hints\">\n                <div>\n                    <p>Najděte sloupec pro kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> tak, že se podíváte na písmena uvedená pod každým sloupcem.</p>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                        graph.barchart.highlightDataPoint( INDEX );\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <p>Porovnejte výšku sloupce s čísly nalevo.</p>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                        graph.barchart.labelDataPoint( INDEX );\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <p>Kolej <var>HOUSES[ INDEX ]</var> obdržela <var>plural( VALUES[ INDEX ], \"house point\" )</var>.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n',	'reading_bar_charts_1',	'2013-04-09 13:57:36'),
(277,	732,	'303.1	 Porozumění sloupcovým grafům 2\n\n303.2	 Podívejte se na graf a odpovězte na otázky:\n\n303.3	 Čí studijní výsledky se v období od pololetí do konce roku nejvíce zlepšily?\n\n303.4	 Sloupec závěrečných výsledků studenta <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> je vyšší než <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            sloupec pololetních výsledků, takže <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> se zlepšil <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>. <var>His( INDEX + 1 )</var> pololetní výsledky byly \r\n                            <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var></code> a <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> závěrečné výsledky byly <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var></code>, takže \r\n                            <var>he( INDEX + 1 )</var> se zlepšil o <code><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code> bodů.\n\n303.5	 Sloupec závěrečných výsledků studenta <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> je nižší než <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                           sloupec pololetních výsledků, takže <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> se nezlepšil <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>.\n\n303.6	 <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is the same height as <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.\n\n303.7	 <var>MOST_IMPROVED</var> improved <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> score the most, scoring <code><var>BEST_IMPROVEMENT</var></code> more points\r\n                        on <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> final exam than on <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> midterm.\n\n303.8	 By how many points did <var>STUDENT</var>\'s score improve from the midterm to the final exam?\n\n303.9	 <span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></span> points\n\n303.10	 Find the two bars for <var>STUDENT</var>.\n\n303.11	 Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s blue bar to the scale on the left to find <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> midterm score.\r\n                            <span data-if=\"MIDTERM[ INDEX ] % 10 === 5\">\r\n                                The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ] - 5</var></code> and <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ] + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                            </span>\r\n                            <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code class=\"hint_blue\"><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var></code> points on the midterm.\n\n303.12	 Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s orange bar to the scale on the left to find <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> final exam score.\r\n                            <span data-if=\"FINAL[ INDEX ] % 10 === 5\">\r\n                                The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ] - 5</var></code> and <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ] + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                            </span>\r\n                            <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code class=\"hint_orange\"><var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var></code> points on the final exam.\n\n303.13	 Subtract the midterm score from the final exam score to find out how much <var>STUDENT</var> improved.\n\n303.14	 <code>\\color{ORANGE}{<var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var>} - \\color{#6495ED}{<var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var>} = <var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code>, so\r\n                        <var>STUDENT</var> improved by <code><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code> points from the midterm to the final exam.\n\n303.15	 How many points did <var>STUDENT</var> earn on the <var>TEST</var>?\n\n303.16	 <span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>ANSWER</var></span> points\n\n303.17	 Find the two bars for <var>STUDENT</var>.\n\n303.18	 Use the key to figure out which of the two bars shows the score for the <var>TEST</var>.\n\n303.19	 Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s <span data-if=\"COLUMN === 0\">blue</span><span data-else>orange</span> bar to the scale on the left.\n\n303.20	 The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>ANSWER - 5</var></code> and <code><var>ANSWER + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                        <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code><var>ANSWER</var></code> points on the <var>TEST</var>.\n\n303.21	 <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code><var>ANSWER</var></code> points on the <var>TEST</var>.\n\n303.22	 How many students improved their scores from the midterm to the final exam?\n\n303.23	 <span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>NUM_IMPROVED</var></span> students\n\n303.24	 <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is taller than <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> improved <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.\n\n303.25	 <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is shorter than <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.\n\n303.26	 <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is the same height as <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.\n\n303.27	 Count the number of students who improved their scores.\n\n303.28	 <code><var>NUM_IMPROVED</var></code> students improved their scores from the midterm to the final exam.\n\n',	'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html data-require=\"math math-format graphie word-problems\">\n<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <title>Porozumění sloupcovým grafům 2</title>\n    <script src=\"../khan-exercise.js\"></script>\n    <style>\n        span.rotate  {\n            -moz-transform: rotate(-90deg);\n            -o-transform: rotate(-90deg);\n            -webkit-transform: rotate(-90deg);\n            -ms-filter: \"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.BasicImage(rotation=3)\";\n        }\n        body.ie span.rotate {\n            left: 60px !important;\n            top: 140px !important;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"exercise\">\n        <div class=\"vars\">\n            <div data-ensure=\"( NUM_IMPROVED >= 3 && !IMPROVE_TIE ) || UNBIASED\">\n                <var id=\"MIDTERM\">$.map( new Array( 5 ), function() { return randRange( 12, 20 ) * 5; } )</var>\n                <var id=\"FINAL\">$.map( new Array( 5 ), function() { return randRange( 12, 20 ) * 5; } )</var>\n                <var id=\"IMPROVEMENT\">$.map( new Array( 5 ), function( e, n ) { return FINAL[ n ] - MIDTERM[ n ]; } )</var>\n                <var id=\"NUM_IMPROVED\">$.map( IMPROVEMENT, function( x ) { return x &gt; 0 ? 1 : null; }).length</var>\n                <var id=\"IMPROVE_TIE\">IMPROVEMENT.slice().sort(function(a,b){return a - b;})[4] === IMPROVEMENT.slice().sort(function(a,b){return a - b;})[3]</var>\n                <var id=\"UNBIASED\">false</var>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"problem\">\n            <p>Podívejte se na graf a odpovězte na otázky:</p>\n            <div class=\"graphie\" id=\"barchart\">\n                init({\n                    range: [ [ -2, 17 ], [ -3, 11 ] ],\n                    scale: [ 30, 30 ]\n                });\n\n                for ( var y = 1; y &lt;= 10; ++y ) {\n                    label( [ 0, y ], y * 10, \"left\", false );\n                    style({ stroke: \"#000\", strokeWidth: 1, opacity: 0.2 }, function() {\n                        line( [ 0, y ], [ 16, y ] )\n                    });\n                }\n                for ( var index = 0; index &lt; 5; ++index ) {\n                    style({ stroke: \"none\", fill: \"#9ab8ed\", opacity: 1.0 });\n                    path([ [ index * 3 + 1, 0 ], [ index * 3 + 1, MIDTERM[ index ] / 10 ], [ index * 3 + 2, MIDTERM[ index ] / 10 ], [ index * 3 + 2, 0 ], [ index * 3 + 1, 0 ] ]);\n                    style({ stroke: \"none\", fill: \"#ffc966\", opacity: 1.0 });\n                    path([ [ index * 3 + 2, 0 ], [ index * 3 + 2, FINAL[ index ] / 10 ], [ index * 3 + 3, FINAL[ index ] / 10 ], [ index * 3 + 3, 0 ], [ index * 3 + 2, 0 ] ]);\n                    style({ opacity: 1.0 });\n                    label( [ index * 3 + 2, 0 ], person( index + 1 ), \"below\", false );\n                }\n                style({ stroke: \"#000\", strokeWidth: 2, opacity: 1.0 });\n                line( [ 0, 0 ], [ 16, 0 ] );\n                line( [ 0, 0 ], [ 0, 10 ] );\n\n                label( [ 8, -0.8 ], \"&lt;b&gt;Student&lt;/b&gt;\", \"below\", false );\n                $( label( [ -1.5, 5 ], \"&lt;b&gt;Score (points)&lt;/b&gt;\", \"center\", false ) ).addClass( \"rotate\" );\n                label( [ 8, 10.5 ], \"&lt;b&gt;Scores on Midterm and Final Exams&lt;/b&gt;\", \"above\", false );\n\n                style({ stroke: \"none\", fill: \"#9ab8ed\", opacity: 1.0 });\n                path([ [ 0, -2 ], [ 0.5, -2  ], [ 0.5, -2.5  ], [ 0, -2.5 ], [ 0, -2 ] ]);\n                style({ stroke: \"#000\", strokeWidth: 2, opacity: 1.0 });\n                label( [ 0.5, -2.25 ], \"Midterm\", \"right\", false );\n                style({ stroke: \"none\", fill: \"#ffc966\", opacity: 1.0 });\n                path([ [ 3, -2 ], [ 3.5, -2  ], [ 3.5, -2.5  ], [ 3, -2.5 ], [ 3, -2 ] ]);\n                style({ stroke: \"#000\", strokeWidth: 2, opacity: 1.0 });\n                label( [ 3.5, -2.25 ], \"Final\", \"right\", false );\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"problems\">\n            <div id=\"most-improved\">\n                <div class=\"vars\">\n                    <var id=\"BEST_IMPROVEMENT\">Math.max.apply( Math, IMPROVEMENT )</var>\n                    <var id=\"MOST_IMPROVED_IDX\">_.indexOf( IMPROVEMENT, BEST_IMPROVEMENT )</var>\n                    <var id=\"MOST_IMPROVED\">person( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"question\">Čí studijní výsledky se v období od pololetí do konce roku nejvíce zlepšily?</p>\n\n                <div class=\"solution\"><var>MOST_IMPROVED</var></div>\n                <ul class=\"choices\" data-category=\"true\">\n                    <li><var>person( 1 )</var></li>\n                    <li><var>person( 2 )</var></li>\n                    <li><var>person( 3 )</var></li>\n                    <li><var>person( 4 )</var></li>\n                    <li><var>person( 5 )</var></li>\n                </ul>\n\n                <div class=\"hints\">\n                    <div data-each=\"5 times as INDEX\">\n                        <div data-if=\"IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ] > 0\">\n                            <p>Sloupec závěrečných výsledků studenta <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> je vyšší než <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            sloupec pololetních výsledků, takže <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> se zlepšil <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>. <var>His( INDEX + 1 )</var> pololetní výsledky byly \r\n                            <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var></code> a <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> závěrečné výsledky byly <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var></code>, takže \r\n                            <var>he( INDEX + 1 )</var> se zlepšil o <code><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code> bodů.</p>\n                            <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                                style({ stroke: GREEN, strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\" });\n                                line( [ INDEX * 3 + 1.5, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 ], [ INDEX * 3 + 2.5, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 ] );\n                                label( [ INDEX * 3 + 1.5, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 + 0.2 ], MIDTERM[ INDEX ], \"below\", false ).css({ fontWeight: \"bold\" });\n                                label( [ INDEX * 3 + 2.5, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 - 0.2 ], FINAL[ INDEX ], \"above\", false ).css({ fontWeight: \"bold\" });\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-else-if=\"IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ] < 0\">\n                            <p>Sloupec závěrečných výsledků studenta <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> je nižší než <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                           sloupec pololetních výsledků, takže <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> se nezlepšil <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>.</p>\n                            <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                                style({ stroke: \"grey\", strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\" });\n                                line( [ INDEX * 3 + 1.5, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 ], [ INDEX * 3 + 2.5, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 ] );\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-else>\n                            <p><var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is the same height as <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p><var>MOST_IMPROVED</var> improved <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> score the most, scoring <code><var>BEST_IMPROVEMENT</var></code> more points\r\n                        on <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> final exam than on <var>his( MOST_IMPROVED_IDX + 1 )</var> midterm.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div id=\"difference\">\n                <div class=\"vars\">\n                    <var id=\"INDEX\" data-ensure=\"IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ] > 0\">randRange( 0, 4 )</var>\n                    <var id=\"STUDENT\">person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"question\">By how many points did <var>STUDENT</var>\'s score improve from the midterm to the final exam?</p>\n\n                <div class=\"solution\" data-type=\"multiple\">\n                    <p><span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></span> points</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"hints\">\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Find the two bars for <var>STUDENT</var>.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: PINK, fill: \"none\", strokeWidth: 2 });\n                            ellipse( [ INDEX * 3 + 2, -0.6 ], [ 1.2, 0.5 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s blue bar to the scale on the left to find <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> midterm score.\r\n                            <span data-if=\"MIDTERM[ INDEX ] % 10 === 5\">\r\n                                The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ] - 5</var></code> and <code><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ] + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                            </span>\r\n                            <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code class=\"hint_blue\"><var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var></code> points on the midterm.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: BLUE, strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\", strokeDasharray: \"-\" });\n                            line( [ INDEX * 3 + 1, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 ], [ 0, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s orange bar to the scale on the left to find <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> final exam score.\r\n                            <span data-if=\"FINAL[ INDEX ] % 10 === 5\">\r\n                                The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ] - 5</var></code> and <code><var>FINAL[ INDEX ] + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                            </span>\r\n                            <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code class=\"hint_orange\"><var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var></code> points on the final exam.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: ORANGE, strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\", strokeDasharray: \"-\" });\n                            line( [ INDEX * 3 + 2, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 ], [ 0, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <p>Subtract the midterm score from the final exam score to find out how much <var>STUDENT</var> improved.</p>\n\n                    <p><code>\\color{ORANGE}{<var>FINAL[ INDEX ]</var>} - \\color{#6495ED}{<var>MIDTERM[ INDEX ]</var>} = <var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code>, so\r\n                        <var>STUDENT</var> improved by <code><var>IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ]</var></code> points from the midterm to the final exam.</p>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div id=\"reading\">\n                <div class=\"vars\">\n                    <var id=\"INDEX\">randRange( 0, 4 )</var>\n                    <var id=\"STUDENT\">person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\n                    <var id=\"COLUMN\">randRange( 0, 1 )</var>\n                    <var id=\"TEST\">[ \"midterm\", \"final exam\" ][ COLUMN ]</var>\n                    <var id=\"ANSWER\">COLUMN === 0 ? MIDTERM[ INDEX ] : FINAL[ INDEX ]</var>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"question\">How many points did <var>STUDENT</var> earn on the <var>TEST</var>?</p>\n\n                <div class=\"solution\" data-type=\"multiple\">\n                    <p><span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>ANSWER</var></span> points</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"hints\">\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Find the two bars for <var>STUDENT</var>.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: PINK, fill: \"none\", strokeWidth: 2 });\n                            ellipse( [ INDEX * 3 + 2, -0.6 ], [ 1.2, 0.5 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Use the key to figure out which of the two bars shows the score for the <var>TEST</var>.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: PINK, fill: \"none\", strokeWidth: 2 });\n                            ellipse( [ COLUMN * 3 + 1.2, -2.25 ], [ 1.5, 0.5 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Compare the height of <var>STUDENT</var>\'s <span data-if=\"COLUMN === 0\">blue</span><span data-else>orange</span> bar to the scale on the left.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                            style({ stroke: PINK, strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\", strokeDasharray: \"-\" });\n                            line( [ INDEX * 3 + 1 + COLUMN, ANSWER / 10 ], [ 0, ANSWER / 10 ] );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p data-if=\"ANSWER % 10 === 5\">The bar\'s height is halfway between <code><var>ANSWER - 5</var></code> and <code><var>ANSWER + 5</var></code>, so\r\n                        <var>STUDENT</var> earned <code><var>ANSWER</var></code> points on the <var>TEST</var>.</p>\n                    <p data-else><var>STUDENT</var> earned <code><var>ANSWER</var></code> points on the <var>TEST</var>.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div id=\"num-improved\">\n                <p class=\"question\">How many students improved their scores from the midterm to the final exam?</p>\n\n                <div class=\"solution\" data-type=\"multiple\">\n                    <p><span style=\"padding-right: 5px\" class=\"sol\" data-forms=\"integer\"><var>NUM_IMPROVED</var></span> students</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"hints\">\n                    <div data-each=\"5 times as INDEX\">\n                        <div data-if=\"IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ] > 0\">\n                            <p><var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is taller than <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> improved <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.</p>\n                            <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"barchart\">\n                                style({ stroke: \"grey\", strokeWidth: 2, arrows: \"-&gt;\" });\n                                line( [ INDEX * 3 + 1.5, MIDTERM[ INDEX ] / 10 ], [ INDEX * 3 + 2.5, FINAL[ INDEX ] / 10 ] );\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-else-if=\"IMPROVEMENT[ INDEX ] < 0\">\n                            <p><var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is shorter than <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-else>\n                            <p><var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var>\'s final exam bar is the same height as <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var>\r\n                            midterm bar, so <var>person( INDEX + 1 )</var> did not improve <var>his( INDEX + 1 )</var> score.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>Count the number of students who improved their scores.</p>\n                    <p><code><var>NUM_IMPROVED</var></code> students improved their scores from the midterm to the final exam.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n',	'reading_bar_charts_2',	'2013-04-09 14:03:39'),
(429,	921,	'368.1	 Určování času\n\n368.2	 Kolik je hodin?\n\n368.3	 Je <span class=\"sol\"><var>HOUR</var></span> : <span class=\"sol\"><var>NICE_MINUTE</var></span> <var>AM_PM</var>\n\n368.4	 dvanáctihodinový čas v hodinách a minutách\n\n368.5	 Malá ručička říká, kolik je hodin, velká ručička určuje, kolik je minut.\n\n368.6	 Hodinová ručička ukazuje na <code><var>HOUR</var></code>, takže je <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.\n\n368.7	 Hodinová ručička je mezi <code><var>HOUR</var></code> a <code><var>HOUR + 1 === 13 ? 1 : HOUR + 1</var></code>, takže je <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.\n\n368.8	 Hodinová ručička se blíží k \r\n <code><var>HOUR + 1 === 13 ? 1 : HOUR + 1</var></code>, ale ještě ji nepřešla, takže je pořád <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.\n\n368.9	 Minutová ručička ukazuje kolmo nahoru, když je <code>0</code> minut, a za hodinu oběhne celý ciferník (čímž projde okolo <code>12</code> čísel za <code>60</code> minut).\n\n368.10	 Za každé číslo, kolem kterého minutová ručička projde, přičtěte <code>\\dfrac{60}{12} = 5</code> minut.\n\n368.11	 Minutová ručička ukazuje na <code><var> (MINUTE / 5) === 0 ? 12: MINUTE / 5 </var></code>, což znamená <span data-if=\"MINUTE === 0\"><code>0</code></span><span data-else><code>5 \\times <var>(MINUTE / 5) === 0 ? 12: MINUTE / 5</var> = <var>MINUTE</var></code></span> minut.\n\n368.12	 Je <code><var>HOUR</var></code>:<code><var>NICE_MINUTE</var></code>.\n\n',	'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html data-require=\"math math-format graphie time\">\n<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <title>Určování času</title>\n    <script src=\"../khan-exercise.js\"></script>\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n        #answer_area .short input[type=text] {\n            width: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"exercise\">\n    <div class=\"vars\">\n        <var id=\"HOUR\">randRange( 1, 12 )</var>\n        <var id=\"MINUTE\">randRange( 0, 11 ) * 5 </var>\n        <var id=\"NICE_MINUTE\"> MINUTE &gt; 5 ? MINUTE : \"0\" + \"\" + MINUTE</var>\n        <var id=\"AM_PM\">HOUR >= 7 ? \"a.m\" : \"p.m.\"</var>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"problems\">\n        <div id=\"analog\">\n            <div class=\"question\">\n                <p>Kolik je hodin?</p>\n                <div class=\"graphie\" id=\"pie\" style=\"float: left;\">\n                    init({ range: [ [-4, 4 ], [ -4, 4 ] ], scale: 25 });\n                    clock = addAnalogClock({ hour: HOUR, minute: MINUTE, minuteTicks: 0, showLabels: false });\n                    clock.draw();\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"graphie\" id=\"digital\" style=\"float: left;\">\n                    init({ range: [ [-5, 5], [-3, 3] ], scale: 25 });\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"solution\" data-type=\"multiple\">\n                <p class=\"short\">Je <span class=\"sol\"><var>HOUR</var></span> : <span class=\"sol\"><var>NICE_MINUTE</var></span> <var>AM_PM</var></p>\n                <p class=\"example\">dvanáctihodinový čas v hodinách a minutách</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"hints\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\">\n                            clock.drawLabels();\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"digital\">\n                        path([ [-3, -1], [3, -1], [3, 1], [-3, 1], [-3, -1] ]);\n                        graph.time = label( [0, -0.1],\n                            \"\\\\Huge{\\\\phantom{00}:\\\\phantom{00}}\",\n                            \"center\" );\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <p>Malá ručička říká, kolik je hodin, velká ručička určuje, kolik je minut.</p>\n                <div>\n                    <p data-if=\"MINUTE <= 10\">Hodinová ručička ukazuje na <code><var>HOUR</var></code>, takže je <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.</p>\n                    <p data-else-if=\"MINUTE > 10  && MINUTE < 45\">Hodinová ručička je mezi <code><var>HOUR</var></code> a <code><var>HOUR + 1 === 13 ? 1 : HOUR + 1</var></code>, takže je <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.</p>\n                    <p data-else>Hodinová ručička se blíží k \r\n <code><var>HOUR + 1 === 13 ? 1 : HOUR + 1</var></code>, ale ještě ji nepřešla, takže je pořád <code><var>HOUR</var></code> hodin.</p>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"digital\">\n                        graph.time.remove();\n                        var padding = HOUR &lt; 10 ? \"\\\\phantom{0}\" : \"\";\n                        graph.time = label([0, -0.1],\n                            \"\\\\Huge{\" + padding + HOUR + \":\\\\phantom{00}}\",\n                            \"center\" );\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <p>Minutová ručička ukazuje kolmo nahoru, když je <code>0</code> minut, a za hodinu oběhne celý ciferník (čímž projde okolo <code>12</code> čísel za <code>60</code> minut).</p>\n                    <p>Za každé číslo, kolem kterého minutová ručička projde, přičtěte <code>\\dfrac{60}{12} = 5</code> minut.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <p>Minutová ručička ukazuje na <code><var> (MINUTE / 5) === 0 ? 12: MINUTE / 5 </var></code>, což znamená <span data-if=\"MINUTE === 0\"><code>0</code></span><span data-else><code>5 \\times <var>(MINUTE / 5) === 0 ? 12: MINUTE / 5</var> = <var>MINUTE</var></code></span> minut.</p>\n                    <div class=\"graphie\" data-update=\"digital\">\n                        graph.time.remove();\n                        var padding = MINUTE &lt; 10 ? \"0\" : \"\";\n                        graph.time = label([0, -0.1],\n                            \"\\\\Huge{\" + HOUR + \":\" + padding + MINUTE + \"}\",\n                            \"center\" );\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <p>Je <code><var>HOUR</var></code>:<code><var>NICE_MINUTE</var></code>.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n',	'telling_time',	'2013-05-09 18:50:06'),
(283,	732,	'163.1	 Zlomky - slovní úlohy 1\n\n163.2	 <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a <var>person( 2 )</var>\r\n                    snědl <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.\n\n163.3	 Pokud původně měli <var>TOTAL</var> kousků, jakou část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> snědli?\n\n163.6	 Snědli <code>\\color{#6495ED}{<var>A + B</var>}</code> z <code><var>TOTAL</var></code> kousků.\n\n163.7	 Snědli <code>\\dfrac{<var>A + B</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.\n\n163.8	 <var>person( 1 )</var> ate <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> of <var>pizza( 1 )</var>, and <var>person( 2 )</var>\r\n                    ate <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.\n\n163.9	 Kdyby zbylo <var>plural(LEFT, \"slice\")</var> , jakou část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> snědli?\n\n163.12	 Protože snědli <var>A + B</var> kousků <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a <var>plural( LEFT, \"slice\" )</var> zbylo,\r\n                        museli na začátku mít <var>TOTAL</var> kousků.\n\n163.13	 Snědli <code>\\color{#6495ED}{<var>A + B</var>}</code> z <code><var>TOTAL</var></code> kousků.\n\n163.14	 Snědli <code>\\dfrac{<var>A + B</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.\n\n163.15	 <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a <var>person( 2 )</var>\r\n                    snědl <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.\n\n163.16	 Pokud <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <code>\\dfrac{<var>A</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> <var>pizza( 1 )</var>,\r\n                    jaká část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> byla celkem snědena?\n\n163.18	 Pokud <var>plural( A, \"slice\")</var> represent<var>A &gt; 1 ? \"\" : \"s\"</var>\r\n                        <code>\\dfrac{<var>A</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>, museli na začátku mít\r\n                        <var>TOTAL</var> kousků.\n\n163.20	 Snědli <code>\\color{#6495ED}{<var>A + B</var>}</code> z <code><var>TOTAL</var></code> kousků.\n\n163.21	 Snědli <code>\\dfrac{<var>A + B</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.\n\n163.22	 <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> of <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a\r\n                    <var>person( 2 )</var> snědl <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.\n\n163.23	 Pokud měli původně <var>TOTAL</var> kousků, jaká část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> zbývá?\n\n163.26	 Dohromady snědli <var>A + B</var> kousků, takže zbylo <var>LEFT</var> kousků z <var>TOTAL</var>.\n\n163.27	 Zbývá <code>\\dfrac{<var>LEFT</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code>  <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.\n\n163.28	 <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a\r\n                    <var>person( 2 )</var> snědl <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.\n\n163.29	 Pokud <var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <code>\\dfrac{<var>A</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> <var>pizza( 1 )</var>,\r\n                    jaká část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> zbývá?\n\n163.31	 Pokud <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> represent<var>A &gt; 1 ? \"\" : \"s\"</var>\r\n                        <code>\\dfrac{<var>A</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>,\r\n                        museli na začátku mít <var>TOTAL</var> kousků.\n\n163.33	 Dohromady snědli <var>A + B</var> kousků, takže zbylo <var>LEFT</var> z <var>TOTAL</var> kousků.\n\n163.34	 Zbývá <code>\\dfrac{<var>LEFT</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.\n\n',	'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html data-require=\"math graphie graphie-helpers word-problems\">\n<head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <title>Zlomky - slovní úlohy 1</title>\n    <script src=\"../khan-exercise.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"exercise\">\n        <div class=\"vars\">\n            <var id=\"A\">randRange( 1, 5 )</var>\n            <var id=\"B\">randRange( 1, 5 )</var>\n            <var id=\"LEFT\">randRange( 1, 5 )</var>\n            <var id=\"TOTAL\">A + B + LEFT</var>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"