 )</var>, museli na začátku mít\r\n                        <var>TOTAL</var> kousků.</p>\n                    <p><code>\\text{fraction of <var>pizza( 1 )</var> eaten} = \\dfrac{\\text{number of slices eaten}}{\\text{number slices total}}</code></p>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Snědli <code>\\color{#6495ED}{<var>A + B</var>}</code> z <code><var>TOTAL</var></code> kousků.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\">\n                            init({\n                                range: [ [-2, 2], [-2, 2] ],\n                                scale: 25\n                            });\n                            var eaten = A + B;\n                            piechart( [ eaten, TOTAL - eaten ], [ \"#6495ED\", \"#FFA500\" ], 2 );\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p>Snědli <code>\\dfrac{<var>A + B</var>}{<var>TOTAL</var>}</code> z <var>pizza( 1 )</var>.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div id=\"show-total-want-left\">\n                <p class=\"problem\"><var>person( 1 )</var> snědl <var>plural( A, \"slice\" )</var> of <var>pizza( 1 )</var> a\r\n                    <var>person( 2 )</var> snědl <var>plural( B, \"slice\" )</var>.</p>\n                <p class=\"question\">Pokud měli původně <var>TOTAL</var> kousků, jaká část <var>pizza( 1 )</var> zbývá?</p>\n                <p class=\"solution\" data-type=\"rational\" data-simplify=\"optional\"><var>LEFT / TOTAL</var></p>\n                <div class=\"hints\">\n                    <p><code>\\text{fraction of <var>pizza( 1 )</var> remaining} = \\dfrac{\\text{number of slices remaining}}{\\text{number slices total}}</code></p>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>Dohromady snědli <var>A + B</var> kousků, takže zbylo <var>LEFT</var> kousků z <var>TOTAL</var>.</p>\n                        <div class=\"graphie\">\n                            init({\n                                range: [ [-2, 